data.content: Tu nombre es [Nombre del usuario]. ¿Hay algo más en lo que pueda ayudarte hoy?
Can you tell me the days of the week in German?

Of course! Here are the days of the week in German:

- Montag (Monday)
- Dienstag (Tuesday)
- Mittwoch (Wednesday)
- Donnerstag (Thursday)
- Freitag (Friday)
- Samstag (Saturday)
- Sonntag (Sunday)

Is there anything else you'd like to know?
